Class TigerTextAccountManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tigertext.ttandroid.account.TigerTextAccountManager

  • public class TigerTextAccountManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains everything relating to an account, such as login, logout, accessing account info, etc.
